lenders.name: Me4Jesus
lenders.occupation: I work for Jesus doing whatever He leads me to do!
lenders.loan_because:
First, the money I loan isn't really "mine", this money has literally come from Jesus Himself.  Everything I currently have is only because of Him so instead of putting my own name here, I want everyone who receives money from this account to thank Jesus Christ because He is the only reason I had it to give in the first place.

I also loan because I know how hard it is out there.  I've been unable to work myself for over 5 years now due to permanent injuries and had no income for about 3 of those years.  In fact, I would be homeless today if it were not for the tender mercy and provision given to me by our dear Lord & Savior Jesus Christ Himself!  I am forever grateful and thankful for His presence in my life and I pray He enters your life too if you don't know Him already.

God has been and continues to be my only help and source of strength and peace through all the troubles life has thrown at me, so I want to use part of what He gives me to help others too.  I'm living proof that we can ALWAYS count on Jesus to provide us with what we "need", just like He told us in the Bible!

To YHVH/Yahshua be all the glory and honor forever and ever!
lenders.occupational_info: I provide free Christian services such as free Christian movies, documentaries, t.v. shows, Bible study software, weekly Bible studies, and MUCH more!  I also provide the latest scientific evidences in all the areas of science (including archeology, geology, creation science, etc.) that show us that the Bible is 100% true and accurate!
